  "2026-06-26T23:12:40.686Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Duplicate check: pm search 'Sentry dependency update @sentry/node @sentry/cli outdated' --status all and pm search 'dependency updates pnpm outdated sentry cli node' --status all found only closed historical dependency tasks plus open release-health/blocker lineages; no active duplicate for the current @sentry/node 10.62.0 and @sentry/cli 3.6.0 refresh."
  "2026-06-26T23:23:45.108Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Evidence: refreshed @sentry/node from 10.61.0 to 10.62.0 and @sentry/cli from 3.5.1 to 3.6.0. GitHub sweep found no open PRs, one open Auto Release issue (#374) still externally blocked on missing RELEASE_PAT, no open Dependabot alerts, no open CodeQL alerts, pnpm audit moderate clean, and pnpm outdated now only reports @types/node 26.x while the repo intentionally targets Node 22 types. Verification passed: pm test pm-4dz7 --run --progress (5/5 linked checks), pnpm typecheck, pnpm quality:static, pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog 2026.6.20 unchanged, package doctor deep ok, pm health summary ok, pm validate history drift ok with known resolution warning backlog, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage 256 files / 5136 tests with 100/100/100/100 coverage, and isolated temp smoke in /tmp/pm-cli-sentry-refresh-smoke-B7XXCD using sandboxed PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH through init/create/claim/update/comments/files/docs/test-run/health/validate/close/release."
